Package: cortex
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern orthodox file manager with dual-panel interface
 Cortex is a fast, cross-platform orthodox file manager inspired by
 Far Manager, with a modern terminal UI. Features include:
 .
  - Dual-panel interface for efficient file management
  - Keyboard-driven navigation with extensive shortcuts
  - Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux)
  - High performance built with Rust
  - Plugin system with Lua scripting
  - Modern TUI with clean, responsive interface